videos.description: Notre Dame RB Dexter Williams takes the handoff and powers into the end zone for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Williams muscles in for TD

videos.description: As Notre Dame sets up for the punt, the snap to Tyler Newsome hits the ground and he can't control it as he gets tackled on fourth down.
videos.headline: Bad snap causes Notre Dame to turn the ball over

videos.description: Notre QB Ian Book tosses a pass towards the right side and Virginia Tech DB Reggie Floyd rises up for the interception.
videos.headline: Floyd jumps to pick off Notre Dame's Book

videos.description: The ball is poked away from Virginia Tech QB Ryan Willis and Notre Dame CB Julian Love scoops it up and returns it to the house.
videos.headline: Notre Dame extends lead with a scoop-and-score

videos.description: Virginia Tech QB Ryan Willis tosses a 3-yard touchdown to WR Damon Hazelton as the Hokies cut their deficit to 17-16.
videos.headline: Willis finds Hazelton for Hokies' first TD of the game

videos.description: Behind a rushing TD by Dexter Williams and a scoop-and-score from Julian Love, Notre Dame holds a 17-16 halftime lead over Virginia Tech.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Notre Dame holds lead at halftime) 2018/10/06 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Notre Dame holds lead at halftime

videos.description: Notre Dame RB Dexter Williams finds a wipe-open hole and speeds 97 yards downfield and into the end zone for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Williams turns corner for 97-yard TD run

videos.description: Notre Dame QB Ian Book flips a pass to WR Miles Boykin, who goes 40 yards to the house for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Book flips it to Boykin on 40-yard TD play

videos.description: Before Virginia Tech hosts Notre Dame, legendary band Metallica delivers a message to hype up Hokies fans before the team runs out on the field.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Metallica hypes up Virginia Tech) 2018/10/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Metallica hypes up Virginia Tech

videos.description: Notre Dame QB Ian Book tosses a 5-yard pass to WR Miles Boykin, who makes the catch for his second touchdown of the game.
videos.headline: Book connects with Boykin again for TD

videos.description: Virginia Tech QB Ryan Willis lobs a 15-yard pass into the end zone to Eric Kumah, who makes the leaping grab for the TD.
videos.headline: Willis floats TD pass to Kumah

videos.description: Notre Dame RB Dexter Williams breaks free and rushes 31 yards into the end zone for his third rushing score of the game.
videos.headline: Williams breaks free for third TD of the game

videos.description: Brian Kelly explains how Notre Dame was able to pull away in the second half and how well QB Ian Book played on the road.
videos.headline: Kelly credits efficiency for Notre Dame's win

videos.description: Notre Dame QB Ian Book explains how he was able to help his team beat Virginia Tech and what it was like playing in that hostile environment.
videos.headline: Book: Game vs. Virginia Tech a 'once in a lifetime' experience
